{"type":"message","id":"d89874cf","parentId":"fc18adb6","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:32:11.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, committed. Now let me give the Lead a summary of the 2 fixes.","thinkingSignature":"51ea075f78fac2fdc5dc565d8caaddb0781061c9c852ded45ac9cb498c3e487c"},{"type":"text","text":"**ДђГЈ fix cбєЈ 2 bug vГ  commit.** TГіm tбєЇt:\n\n### Bug 1: Confluence credentials khГґng apply вњ…\n- **NguyГЄn nhГўn:** `applyCredentials` chб»‰ set `CONF_TOKEN`, bб»Џ qua `CONF_BASE_URL` + `CONF_USERNAME`\n- **Fix:** Hб»Џi Д‘б»§ 3 trЖ°б»ќng (URL + email + token), apply Д‘б»§ 3 vГ o mб»Ќi confluence MCP server\n\n### Bug 2: `curl | bash` treo б»џ prompt y/n вњ…\n- **NguyГЄn nhГўn:** stdin bб»‹ curl chiбєїm в†’ inquirer khГґng Д‘б»Ќc Д‘Ж°б»Јc\n- **Fix:**\n  - `install.sh`: tб»± detect piped mode в†’ thГЄm `--yes`\n  - `ahv-setup.js`: piped mode tб»± default team = `dev` (khГґng prompt)\n- **DГ№ng pipe vб»›i team cб»Ґ thб»ѓ:**\n  ```bash\n  curl -fsSL .../install.sh | bash -s dev   # team dev\n  curl -fsSL .../install.sh | bash -s ba    # team ba\n  curl -fsSL .../install.sh | bash -s qa    # team qa\n  ```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":187,"output":290,"cacheRead":68118,"cacheWrite":458,"totalTokens":69053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776256323848,"responseId":"062eb8458cd6494c44996ef4818bec8f"}}
