{"type":"message","id":"e3de6983","parentId":"ed953780","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:32:27.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent couldn't send the Telegram message because there's no Telegram messaging tool available. The Telegram session is done but delivery failed. I need to inform the user about this issue with the Telegram group message from the cron session.\n\nThe original message was supposed to be sent to Telegram group -5163901258. Since direct messaging via sessions_send timed out and the subagent couldn't help, I need to let the user know.\n\nActually, looking at the original task - this was an inter-session message from the cron session asking me to forward a message. The cron session is trying to send an update to the DTLX group. Since Telegram delivery isn't working (gateway timeout issues), I should let the user know.","thinkingSignature":"72445cf1f9772f615114e9ab0470c64f1d9d67249c1c460ce8956a14822b0244"},{"type":"text","text":"Telegram delivery vбє«n khГґng hoбєЎt Д‘б»™ng вЂ” subagent confirm khГґng cГі Telegram tool trong toolkit hiб»‡n tбєЎi.\n\n**TГіm tбєЇt tГ¬nh trбєЎng:**\n- Gateway consistently timeout khi gб»­i Telegram\n- `sessions_send` в†’ timeout\n- Spawn subagent в†’ khГґng cГі Telegram messaging API\n\n**Message cбє§n gб»­i (tб»« cron DTLX):**\n> рџџЎ Orbis-DTLX вЂ” 15p Update | 12:25 UTC 15 Apr\n> Changes: RESUMED cron DTLX + main orchestrator\n> Pipeline: HEALTHY вњ…\n\nNбєїu cбє§n gб»­i thГґng bГЎo nГ y, cГі 2 lб»±a chб»Ќn:\n1. **TбєЎm thб»ќi:** Gб»­i thб»§ cГґng tб»« Telegram bot / paste vГ o group\n2. **Fix dГ i hбєЎn:** CбєҐu hГ¬nh Telegram MCP server cho phГ©p gб»­i outbound messages"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":363,"cacheRead":6864,"cacheWrite":57173,"totalTokens":64400,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776256335723,"responseId":"062e