{"type":"message","id":"79c0bada","parentId":"c55ae3bc","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:52:29.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The committed configs use `CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL`, `CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN`, `CONFLUENCE_EMAIL` (wrong env var names). My earlier `applyCredentials` fix in `bin/ahv-setup.js` sets `CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_TOKEN`, `CONF_USERNAME` (correct for the confluence-mcp-server). But the template still has the wrong names.\n\nSo I need to fix the configs to use the correct env var names that the `confluence-mcp-server` actually expects: `CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_TOKEN`, `CONF_USERNAME`.","thinkingSignature":"16ef67ae98a1f5071105208d1ed29157761d6d6742c6b63fbfa12adf465b1a27"},{"type":"text","text":"Committed configs vбє«n dГ№ng sai env names (`CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL` thay vГ¬ `CONF_BASE_URL`). Fix tбєҐt cбєЈ:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_trws3sxtkvkv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && python3 -c \"\nimport json, os\n\nfor fname in ['configs/team-dev.json', 'configs/team-ba.json', 'configs/team-qa.json']:\n    d = json.load(open(fname))\n    changed = []\n    mcp = d.get('mcp', {})\n    servers = mcp.get('servers', {})\n    for key in servers:\n        env = servers[key].get('env', {})\n        # Map old -> new\n        if 'CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL' in env:\n            env['CONF_BASE_URL'] = env.pop('CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL')\n            changed.append(key + ': CONF_BASE_URL')\n        if 'CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN' in env:\n            env['CONF_TOKEN'] = env.pop('CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN')\n            changed.append(key + ': CONF_TOKEN')\n        if 'CONFLUENCE_EMAIL' in env:\n            env['CONF_USERNAME'] = env.pop('CONFLUENCE_EMAIL')\n            changed.append(key + ': CONF_USERNAME')\n    if changed:\n        with open(fname, 'w') as f:\n            json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n        print(fname + ':', ', '.join(changed))\n    else:\n        print(fname + ': no changes')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":192,"output":462,"cacheRead":164424,"cacheWrite":761,"totalTokens":165839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776257540882,"responseId":"062ebd060e62715e9ffbae5bf4abfbdd"}}
