{"type":"message","id":"8c97a464","parentId":"7c395d74","timestamp":"2026-04-16T01:43:25.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The unpack script looks correct now. Manifest entries are `{agent}/{filename}` (e.g., `agile-product-owner/AGENTS.md`). The script strips the agent prefix to get `AGENTS.md`, then writes to `destDir/AGENTS.md` = `~/.openclaw/skills/agile-product-owner/AGENTS.md`. \n\nWait, but `destDir` is `homePath` which is `~/.openclaw/`. So:\n- `filePath = path.join(homePath, relativePath)` = `~/.openclaw/AGENTS.md`\n\n\n- That's wrong! Skills should go to `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/`\n\nI see the issue now вЂ” the unpacked files are going directly to `~/.openclaw/` instead of being nested under `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/`. The skills should live in a subdirectory structure, but the current path construction skips that entirely.\n\nLooking at the manifest entries like `agile-product-owner/SOUL.md`, the intent is clearly to have them organized as `~/.openclaw/skills/agile-product-owner/SOUL.md`. The script is extracting the agent prefix correctly but not prepending the `skills/` directory when writing the files out.\n\nI need to modify the path construction to insert `skills/` between the destination directory and the relative path, so files end up in the proper `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/` structure instead of directly in `~/.openclaw/`.","thinkingSignature":"fcdba96fc39d3b2d4f1879b63055fffa7fec96697468b25be24fc6fcbe56c093"},{"type":"text","text":"Unpack script viбєїt sai Д‘Ж°б»ќng вЂ” bб»Џ qua `skills/` subdir. Fix Д‘Гєng:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dk52ecf8yzns_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js","edits":[{"oldText":"      const agentPrefix = entry.file.split(\"/\")[0] + \"/\";\n      const relativePath = entry.file.startsWith(agentPrefix)\n        ? entry.file.slice(agentPrefix.length) : entry.file;\n      const filePath = path.join(destDir, relativePath);","newText":"      const agentPrefix = entry.file.split(\"/\")[0] + \"/\";\n      const relativePath = entry.file.startsWith(agentPrefix)\n        ? entry.file.slice(agentPrefix.length) : entry.file;\n      // Skills go under destDir/skills/{agent}/ вЂ” e.g. ~/.openclaw/skills/senior-backend/SOUL.md\n      const filePath = path.join(destDir, \"skills\", entry.file);"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":962,"output":553,"cacheRead":42838,"cacheWrite":285,"totalTokens":44638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776303792641,"responseId":"062f71b1c63bd25b389373222b9dfe62"}}
