{"type":"message","id":"140b3a5d","parentId":"20c5d2dd","timestamp":"2026-04-16T01:43:33.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, that would produce `~/.openclaw/skills/agile-product-owner/SOUL.md` which is correct! But I also need to update the console.log path. Let me also update the path shown to the user.\n\nActually, let me also check if the old `skills.pack` (efb7680) had manifest entries with `skills/agile-product-owner/SKILL.md` format. If so, the old unpack script that was using `path.join(destDir, \"skills\", relativePath)` would have produced `~/.openclaw/skills/skills/agile-product-owner/SKILL.md` which is double-nested. \n\nSo the old manifest with `agile-product-owner/skills/agile-product-owner/SKILL.md` format was definitely wrong, and my fix to strip the agent prefix and write directly to the skills directory is the right approach. Let me commit this change and test it out.","thinkingSignature":"bbca8863fad9fa5a9f5de6d539a2807645d75e4b96fdc8533b5c73564d4b7fd3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bktosn5mumsn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && node --check bin/ahv-setup.js && echo \"вњ… Syntax OK\" && bash -n install.sh && echo \"вњ… install.sh OK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":175,"output":263,"cacheRead":42987,"cacheWrite":1526,"totalTokens":44951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776303805772,"responseId":"062f71bed45836995d17d4b6c774b159"}}
