{"type":"message","id":"9529d978","parentId":"7e75d313","timestamp":"2026-04-16T01:55:41.384Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'll add the `buildAnswersFromEnv` function right before `collectCredentials`.","thinkingSignature":"f9ceb21fa0d22f36e6347718cea7330a8084c84406c9eba584057e37feb2b7d3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qzg9bf7lymzm_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js","edits":[{"oldText":"// в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Collect credentials в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ","newText":"// в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Build answers from env vars (pipe/non-TTY mode) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nfunction buildAnswersFromEnv(team) {\n  const required = REQUIRED_CREDS[team] || [];\n  const answers = { openclawPath: process.env.OPENCLAW_HOME || \"$HOME/.openclaw\" };\n\n  for (const cred of required) {\n    switch (cred) {\n      case \"AHV_API_KEY\":\n        answers.ahvApiKey = process.env.AHVHOLDING_API_KEY || \"\";\n        break;\n      case \"GITLAB_TOKEN\":\n        answers.gitlabToken = process.env.GITLAB_TOKEN || \"\";\n        answers.gitlabUrl   = process.env.GITLAB_URL || \"https://gitlab.com\";\n        break;\n      case \"CONF_TOKEN\":\n        answers.confUrl   = process.env.CONFLUENCE_URL   || \"https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki\";\n        answers.confEmail = process.env.CONFLUENCE_EMAIL || \"\";\n        answers.confToken = process.env.CONFLUENCE_TOKEN || \"\";\n        break;\n      case \"STITCH_API_KEY\":\n        answers.stitchKey = process.env.STITCH_API_KEY || \"\";\n        break;\n      case \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\":\n        answers.telegramBot = process.env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN || \"\";\n        break;\n    }\n  }\n  return answers;\n}\n\n// в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Collect credentials в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":150,"output":437,"cacheRead":63827,"cacheWrite":666,"totalTokens":65080,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776304532657,"responseId":"062f749608c73789b01d9f7f8b8f72ae"}}
