{"type":"message","id":"7477290a","parentId":"b2a4a58f","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:16:56.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The remote `feat/full-setup-mcp` is now at a24ae7f, which is 52e1911..a24ae7f (7 commits ahead of 52e1911). But the local `HEAD` in the clone is at e051831, which is between b98efa6 and 23d955a. So the local clone is not at the latest.\n\nThe issue is that the install.sh did `git pull origin feat/full-setup-mcp` but the local `HEAD` is not at `feat/full-setup-mcp` - it might be detached or on a different branch.\n\nWait - actually looking at the `git pull` output: it pulled from `origin feat/full-setup-mcp` but the local `HEAD` was at e051831. \n\nThe problem is the clone from the main branch doesn't automatically switch to the feat branch, so when I tried to pull from feat/full-setup-mcp, the local branch didn't exist yet or was pointing to a different commit. I need to make sure the install.sh either checks out the feat branch first or pulls directly into the current branch if it exists.\n\nActually, I can combine these operations into a single command that fetches from the remote branch and resets the local branch to match it.","thinkingSignature":"005a018d1e795104c403e25253d8b0d85b53a2401e6ccffba0f9bb912df74ecb"},{"type":"text","text":"Clone tб»« `main` nhЖ°ng pull tб»« `feat/...` вЂ” branch mismatch. Fix luГґn trong install.sh:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dll1r6zwix4n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && python3 - << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('install.sh', 'rb') as f:\n    raw = f.read()\n\nold_pull = b'''    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git pull origin feat/full-setup-mcp --quiet'''\n\nnew_pull = b'''    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git fetch origin feat/full-setup-mcp && git reset --hard origin/feat/full-setup-mcp'''\n\nif old_pull in raw:\n    raw = raw.replace(old_pull, new_pull)\n    print('вњ… pull updated')\nelse:\n    print('вќЊ not found')\n\nwith open('install.sh', 'wb') as f:\n    f.write(raw)\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":424,"output":477,"cacheRead":131087,"cacheWrite":751,"totalTokens":132739,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776309403287,"responseId":"062f879cb7d80f75e9723769479a9ff2"}}
